          div.circle(style="background-image:url('/img/sport-circle.jpg')")
          img.icon
      //- Events
      section.slice.sell
        .text
          h2 There's an event for you
          p Whether you like to club, network, or visit a London attraction, there is always something for you. 
          p Regular events include a weekly Monday Nights Madness evening at The Loft student bar, as well as Let’s Go adventures around London. 
          p Plus our upcoming Arrivals Week is not far away – and this isn’t your usual freshers.
        .imagery
          div.bg(style="background-image:url('/img/events-bg.jpg')")
            svg(version="1.1" id="Layer_1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 120 120" style="enable-background:new 0 0 120 120;" xml:space="preserve")
