          div.circle(style="background-image:url('/img/advice-circle.jpg')")
          img.icon
      //- Hero section
      section.slice#last
        .text
          h1 It's decision time...
          p Get started now so you can buy tickets to Arrivals Week, join sports and societies and stay in the loop.
